The studio has also embraced the format of [original net animations](/Original_net_animation) (ONAs), specifically tailored for digital distribution platforms. This allows for direct engagement with online audiences, often leveraging established franchises for broader appeal. It's a pragmatic approach to content delivery in the digital age.

